      <title>乌克兰的债券随着特朗普的争执席卷东欧交易而下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/ukraine-bonds-drop-as-trump-feud-shakes-up-east-european-trades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自去年重组以来，乌克兰的美元债券是美国和欧洲对和平进程之间的分裂以来最多的，这使投资者期望有序地朝着停火前进。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/ukraine-bonds-drop-as-trump-feud-shakes-up-east-european-trades</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 09:13:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非最大的政党任命新的经济政策负责人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/south-africa-s-biggest-party-appoints-new-economic-policy-chief</link>
      <description><![CDATA[非洲国民大会是南非最大的政党，在对其内部结构进行大修中任命Zuko Godlimpi为经济转型委员会的负责人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/south-africa-s-biggest-party-appoints-new-economic-policy-chief</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 09:03:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民意调查发现，加拿大人在消费者抗议中避开亚马逊</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/canadians-shun-amazon-in-consumer-protest-against-us-poll-finds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大多数加拿大消费者表示，自美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）升级他对加拿大的威胁以来，他们已经退缩了购买美国制造的产品，并且在Amazon.com Inc.上购物。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/canadians-shun-amazon-in-consumer-protest-against-us-poll-finds</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗副总统贾瓦德·扎里夫（Javad Zarif）辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/iran-s-vice-president-javad-zarif-resigns-from-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在议会罢免财政部长后的第二天，伊朗的资深外交官穆罕默德·贾瓦德·扎里夫（Mohammad Javad Zarif）辞去了副总统，这表明伊斯兰共和国的硬林和温和派之间的裂痕越来越大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/iran-s-vice-president-javad-zarif-resigns-from-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 07:50:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>《全球时报》说</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/china-may-target-us-crops-in-tariff-response-global-times-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《全球时报》报道，中国正在考虑针对特朗普政府的关税，该报复措施原定于周二生效。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/china-may-target-us-crops-in-tariff-response-global-times-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 04:38:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲竞选制定计划，以拯救Zelenskiy和美国的支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-02/europe-races-to-craft-plan-to-save-zelenskiy-and-us-support</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国总理凯尔·斯泰默（Keir Starmer）和其他欧洲领导人在伦敦举行的安全峰会向乌克兰展示了广泛的支持。不过，在幕后，他们争先恐后地将Volodymyr Zelenskiy与美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）返回桌子。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-02/europe-races-to-craft-plan-to-save-zelenskiy-and-us-support</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Mar 2025 23:02:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙告诉法国菲加罗，英国制作乌克兰休战计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-02/france-uk-working-on-one-month-truce-in-ukraine-macron-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统伊曼纽尔·马克龙（Emmanuel Macron）和英国总理凯尔·斯塔默（Keir Starmer）正在制定一项计划在乌克兰进行一个月的休战计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-02/france-uk-working-on-one-month-truce-in-ukraine-macron-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Mar 2025 22:10:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列对哈马斯的立场强化了，特朗普勇敢地</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-02/israel-signals-hardened-stance-toward-hamas-emboldened-by-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列决定在一年多以来首次切除对加沙的人道主义援助，这表明该组织拒绝了美国领导的停火提议，对哈马斯的零容忍态度提出了新的零容忍态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-02/israel-signals-hardened-stance-toward-hamas-emboldened-by-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Mar 2025 16:57:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚前总理伊斯梅尔（Ismail）以嫁接调查命名</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-02/malaysia-ex-prime-minister-ismail-named-in-graft-investigation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚反腐败委员会正在调查涉及前总理伊斯梅尔·萨布里·亚科布（Ismail Sabri Yaakob）的嫁接和洗钱指控，后者成为东南亚国家的最新前领导人，以涉嫌嫁接。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-02/malaysia-ex-prime-minister-ismail-named-in-graft-investigation</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Mar 2025 12:49:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普认为Zelenskiy是问题，乌克兰人坚持在他身边</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-02/trump-sees-zelenskiy-as-the-problem-but-ukrainians-stick-by-him</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的政府明确表示，沃尔迪米尔·泽伦斯基（Volodymyr Zelenskiy）是帮助乌克兰的障碍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-02/trump-sees-zelenskiy-as-the-problem-but-ukrainians-stick-by-him</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Mar 2025 07:14:06 GMT</pubDate>
